OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1779109902
OL,3,C'Gold plating' HS2 resulted in
OL,4,Crailway's woes
OL,6,F"Gold plating" HS2, including by
OL,7,Ffocusing on achieving the "highest
OL,8,Fpossible speeds" for the railway, are
OL,9,Famong the faults which contributed to
OL,10,Fthe project's woes, a major review is
OL,11,Fexpected to find.
OL,13,FSir Stephen Lovegrove, the former
OL,14,Fnational security adviser, will
OL,15,Fcriticise the "original sins" in the
OL,16,Fdecision-making behind the
OL,17,Fmultibillion-pound rail project in a
OL,18,Freport due to be published this week.
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@NO]oD@[OUpD@PO]wD@OOUwD@]O]
