FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1779109902
OL,3,C'Gold plating' HS2 resulted in
OL,4,Crailway's woes
OL,6,FThe review comes as Transport
OL,7,FSecretary Heidi Alexander will set out
OL,8,Fnew costs and a timetable for the
OL,9,Fstripped back version of HS2, which is
OL,10,Fstill being built between London and
OL,11,FBirmingham.
OL,13,FIn March, she tasked the new CEO of
OL,14,FHS2, Mark Wild, with finding ways to
OL,15,Fsave the taxpayer cash and speed up
OL,16,Fconstruction time, including by
OL,17,Freducing the speed of trains.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1779109902
OL,3,C'Gold plating' HS2 resulted in
OL,4,Crailway's woes
OL,6,FHS2 was originally designed to run at
OL,7,F360km per hour, faster than any trains
OL,8,Fin the world. Ministers are now
OL,9,Fconsidering reducing this to 320km per
OL,10,Fhour as part of steps to build it out
OL,11,Ffaster.
OL,13,FIn his review of the project, Sir
OL,14,FStephen is expected to list "the
OL,15,Foriginal sins of the scheme",
OL,16,Fincluding "the original 'gold plating'
OL,17,Fof the high-speed concept, with a
OL,18,Ffocus on the highest possible speeds,
OL,19,Fresulting in bespoke and highly
OL,20,Fengineered design".
OL,26,@vD@]OUwD@\O]xD@KOU|D@RO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
