FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1779109902
OL,3,C'Gold plating' HS2 resulted in
OL,4,Crailway's woes
OL,6,FHe will also hit out at "the decision
OL,7,Fto begin construction at the hardest
OL,8,Fpoints of the route" between London
OL,9,Fand the Midlands.
OL,11,F"Changing objectives and political
OL,12,Fpriorities", as well as the level of
OL,13,Fcosts and risk "being very badly
OL,14,Funderestimated" are also set to come
OL,15,Funder fire in the report.
OL,26,@nD@YOUpD@TO]sD@AOUtD@KO]uD@POUvD@OO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
