PN,40205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1779109902
OL,3,C'Gold plating' HS2 resulted in
OL,4,Crailway's woes
OL,6,FA Government source said: "The
OL,7,FLovegrove Report further confirms the
OL,8,Fastonishing extent to which previous
OL,9,FConservative governments had totally
OL,10,Flost control of HS2, frittering
OL,11,Fbillions of taxpayer's money away and
OL,12,Fleaving the project no closer to being
OL,13,Ffinished than when it started.
OL,15,F"It has been a sorry mess, but this
OL,16,FGovernment has done the hard yards to
OL,17,Fpull the project out of the dirt and
OL,18,Fdeliver the better connections that
OL,19,Fhave long been promised to the
OL,20,Fmidlands.
OL,26,@nD@[OUwD@AOU
